metadata.name: ALLURING ATTRACTION
metadata.description:
This is a 1/1 NFT in the collection

The alluring attraction, that female "mystery,
when a woman is attracted and it is unclear why - she is attracted and that's it. 

Have you experienced the pain of parting or the joy of meeting? Are you close to feelings of awe or hope?

Self-love, for me, is first and foremost freedom.

Freedom from unnecessary thoughts, from unnecessary actions.

By accepting and loving myself, I learned to concentrate more on what I like and what really matters.

By choosing myself, I learned to truly be happy, regardless of my circumstances. It opened me up and showed me my soul.
